ed hybrid model opens a new avenue to explore the complicated\ninteractions encountered in discrete particle dynamics that involve the\nformation of force chains, particle interlocking, particle attrition, wear, and\nthe eventual breakage.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2020 16:32:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Feb 2021 21:31:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-25"}
