anckian scenario and it determines the whole\nplot until the total extinction of the universe. We will show that {\\it\ninformation}, besides not being born of the universe, also does not develop\nfrom it like the computational idea of Artificial Intelligence (AI). Thus, the\nuniverse is not simply self-taught as defended by the spontaneous creation.\nThis could shed light on the problem of Penrose's Weyl curvature hypothesis,\nwhich considers a null Weyl curvature due to a null entropy in the big bang.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2020 21:35:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-16"}
